{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Blow up your enemies!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232520/extras/Gif1PlayOptimized.gif?t=1740255435\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blasted Dice is roguelike deckbuilder where you have a launcher that shoots explosive dice. As you play through rounds, you acquire different dice and items that aid you in doing more damage to your enemies, or blocking from their attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Acquire powerful dice!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232520/extras/dices.gif?t=1740255435\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Assemble a deck of 9 different varieties of dice, each one with different effects on your score. Use that score to damage enemies or block from their attacks. Playing various combinations of dice form combos that boost your score even higher.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Discover a variety of items!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232520/extras/gifItems.gif?t=1740255435\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">9 different types of dice with unique abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">100+ items that enhance your score or add new abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10 different dice combo types which further boost your score</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A cool cow</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A loyal dog</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And endless replayability!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.